      <title>前端小技巧</title>
      <link href="/articles/d688a938.html"/>
      <url>/articles/d688a938.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer"><h2 id="嵌套注释"><a href="#嵌套注释" class="headerlink" title="嵌套注释"></a>嵌套注释</h2><p>情况说明：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在已经注释的语句外面在注释，可能会报错</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>插件<code>Nested Comments</code></p><p>快捷方式<code>ctrl</code>+<code>alt</code>+<code>/</code></p><h2 id="vscode-快捷键"><a href="#vscode-快捷键" class="headerlink" title="vscode 快捷键"></a>vscode 快捷键</h2><ul><li><code>ctrl</code>+<code>R</code> 快速打开最近的文件</li><li><code>ctrl</code>+<code>K</code> 删除当前行</li></ul><h2 id="CSS-实现多个容器保持相同宽度"><a href="#CSS-实现多个容器保持相同宽度" class="headerlink" title="CSS 实现多个容器保持相同宽度"></a>CSS 实现多个容器保持相同宽度</h2><p>👉 <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UW4y117sN?spm_id_from=444.41.list.card_archive.click&vd_source=9c3ca6e3d6382b58d1344b4a3e6f1533">视频</a></p><blockquote><p>前提：flex 布局会让容器保持相同的高度</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;display: inline-flex; flex-direction: column&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;s1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;background-color: green&quot;</span> <span class="attr">contenteditable</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span>213<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;s2&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;background-color: green&quot;</span>&gt;</span>dawidbaw<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><details>    <summary style="background: #ebf9ed">关键</summary>    <b style="font-size: 20px;">        style="display: inline-flex; flex-direction: column"    </b></details><br><blockquote><p>当 Flex Box 容器没有设置宽度大小限制时，当 display 指定为 flex 时，FlexBox 的宽度会&#x3D;&#x3D;填充&#x3D;&#x3D;父容器，当 display 指定为 inline-flex 时，FlexBox 的宽度会&#x3D;&#x3D;包裹&#x3D;&#x3D;子 Item，</p></blockquote><h2 id="导航栏排列"><a href="#导航栏排列" class="headerlink" title="导航栏排列"></a>导航栏排列</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">float</span>: left;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>div 中的元素按左排列</p><h2 id="位置调度"><a href="#位置调度" class="headerlink" title="位置调度"></a>位置调度</h2><h3 id="方法一"><a href="#方法一" class="headerlink" title="方法一"></a>方法一</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">position</span>:relative;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">margin-top</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="方法二"><a href="#方法二" class="headerlink" title="方法二"></a>方法二</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">position</span>:absolute;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">top</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="垂直水平居中"><a href="#垂直水平居中" class="headerlink" title="垂直水平居中"></a>垂直水平居中</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">display</span>: grid;</span><br><span class="line">place-items: center; //对要求居中的元素的父类进行该设置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="图片缝隙"><a href="#图片缝隙" class="headerlink" title="图片缝隙"></a>图片缝隙</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">img</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: block;</span><br><span class="line">  //或者</span><br><span class="line">  //<span class="attribute">vertical-align</span>:top;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">//再</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-tag">body</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="按钮特效"><a href="#按钮特效" class="headerlink" title="按钮特效"></a>按钮特效</h2><h3 id="渐变色"><a href="#渐变色" class="headerlink" title="渐变色"></a>渐变色</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">10%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="动画帧"><a href="#动画帧" class="headerlink" title="动画帧"></a>动画帧</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@keyframes</span> btn-anim1 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">10%</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">10%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">30%</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> blueviolet;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">30%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">50%</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> orangered;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">50%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">70%</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> cornflowerblue;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">70%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">90%</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">box-shadow</span>: <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="number">5px</span> aquamarine;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="built_in">linear-gradient</span>(to right, black <span class="number">90%</span>, <span class="number">#5691c8</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="引入动画"><a href="#引入动画" class="headerlink" title="引入动画"></a>引入动画</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">animation</span>: btn-anim1 <span class="number">2s</span> infinite;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="fullPage-js"><a href="#fullPage-js" class="headerlink" title="fullPage.js"></a>fullPage.js</h2><p>一个翻页效果的 jquery 插件</p><h3 id="引入"><a href="#引入" class="headerlink" title="引入"></a>引入</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;js/jquery-3.6.0.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;js/fullpage.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h3><p>代码包含在一个<div id ="fullpage">里，每个页面 div 后面加上 class 名为 section，调用 jquery</p><p>如图所示</p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/1e39356de1283692a950a520798a50c1fa4f0799.png" alt="image-20220117154550437"></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">  $(<span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">    $(<span class="string">&quot;#fullpage&quot;</span>).<span class="title function_">fullpage</span>();</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript">  &#125;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-javascript"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Swiper-js"><a href="#Swiper-js" class="headerlink" title="Swiper.js"></a>Swiper.js</h2><p>官方网站 <a href="https://swiperjs.com/get-started">https://swiperjs.com/get-started</a></p><p>css 引用放在 head</p><p>js 引用放在 body</p><h2 id="CSS-定位布局"><a href="#CSS-定位布局" class="headerlink" title="CSS 定位布局"></a>CSS 定位布局</h2><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ni4y1g7tc?from=search&amp;seid=5551797381222029782&amp;spm_id_from=333.337.0.0">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ni4y1g7tc?from=search&amp;seid=5551797381222029782&amp;spm_id_from=333.337.0.0</a></p><p>子绝父相，意思是子元素绝对定位 absolute，父元素相对定位 relative</p><h3 id="relative"><a href="#relative" class="headerlink" title="relative"></a>relative</h3><p>relative 是相对之前所在位置进行偏移，不脱离文档流</p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/0096d27f1d2bd85626ae38a40aea728a5e7a86e8.png" alt="image-20220121160413075"></p><h3 id="absolute"><a href="#absolute" class="headerlink" title="absolute"></a>absolute</h3><p>absolute 是对有着 relative 定位的父元素或者是 html 的位置进行偏移，脱离文档流，后面的元素会挤占它的空间，它会在挤占它的元素的上方</p><p>相对于有相对定位的父盒子偏移，父盒子没有相对定位就一直向上查找，直到 body</p><p>可实现叠加效果，不规则位置</p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/b3a2cfa08cd82550d62a118c84114a237824e217.png" alt="image-20220121160641414"></p><h3 id="z-index"><a href="#z-index" class="headerlink" title="z-index"></a>z-index</h3><p>z-index 属性指定了一个元素的堆叠顺序（哪个元素应该放在前面，或后面）</p><p>数字越大，元素就越在前面</p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/7046495d3fb07f57896d13ffbfff82064e1f727d.png" alt="image-20220121162847592"></p><h3 id="sticky"><a href="#sticky" class="headerlink" title="sticky"></a>sticky</h3><p><a href="https://www.runoob.com/try/try.php?filename=trycss_position_sticky">https://www.runoob.com/try/try.php?filename=trycss_position_sticky</a></p><p>粘性定位，可以看做是 relative 和 fixed 的结合</p><p>粘性定位的元素是依赖于用户的滚动，在 <strong>position:relative</strong> 与 <strong>position:fixed</strong> 定位之间切换。</p><p>它的行为就像 <strong>position:relative;</strong> 而当页面滚动超出目标区域时，它的表现就像 **position:fixed;**，它会固定在目标位置。</p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/0a23286748e00c74a13eb0aa23f6bc09045a86c1.png" alt="image-20220121162507965"></p><p><img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/album/d6e4e025fbad50cf3b70be36b9c61ccc74257544.png" alt="image-20220121162522315"></p><h2 id="a-标签内部跳转"><a href="#a-标签内部跳转" class="headerlink" title="a 标签内部跳转"></a>a 标签内部跳转</h2><p>要创建内部链接，你需要将链接的 <code>href</code> 属性值设置为一个哈希符号 <code>#</code> 加上你想内部链接到的元素的 <code>id</code></p><p>如：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#contacts-header&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Contacts<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="History-Api"><a href="#History-Api" class="headerlink" title="History Api"></a>History Api</h2><ul><li>history.back( ) 返回</li><li>history.forward( ) 前进</li><li>history.go(0) 刷新</li><li>history.go(正数) 前进几</li><li>history.go(负数) 后退几</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
