      <title>hexo+豆瓣插件</title>
      <link href="/articles/0.html"/>
      <url>/articles/0.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Hexo博客添加豆瓣插件"><a href="#Hexo博客添加豆瓣插件" class="headerlink" title="Hexo博客添加豆瓣插件"></a>Hexo博客添加豆瓣插件</h1><p>        <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Typora-v0.11.18-green?style=for-the-badge">    <a href="https://github.com/mumuxi176"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85-mumuxi176-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=github"></a></p><blockquote><p>前言：nodeJs版本过高（比如v16.x）会导致豆瓣的电影、书籍等资源内容无法加载，推荐使用v12.x</p></blockquote><h2 id="效果"><a href="#效果" class="headerlink" title="效果"></a>效果</h2><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ngffrgy1h4syjc2lxxj327z1674qq.jpg" alt="image.png"></p><h2 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-douban --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h2><h3 id="博客配置文件"><a href="#博客配置文件" class="headerlink" title="博客配置文件"></a>博客配置文件</h3><p>在<code>_config.yml中</code>添加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">douban:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">user:</span> <span class="string">XXXXXXX</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">builtin:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># 选择是否有主题渲染</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">book:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;This is my book title&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">quote:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;This is my book quote&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">movie:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;This is my movie title&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">quote:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;This is my movie quote&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ngffrgy1h4sya0ic5fj31vu0d8jwl.jpg" alt="image.png"></p><h3 id="豆瓣id"><a href="#豆瓣id" class="headerlink" title="豆瓣id"></a>豆瓣id</h3><p>登录豆瓣个人主页，在<code>上方网址栏</code>中的<code>https://www.douban.com/people/xxxxxx/</code>，其中xxx就是豆瓣id</p><h2 id="运行命令"><a href="#运行命令" class="headerlink" title="运行命令"></a>运行命令</h2><p><code>hexo clean</code></p><p><code>hexo douban</code></p><p><code>hexo g</code></p><p><code>hexo s</code></p><p><code>hexo deploy</code></p><blockquote><p>一开始是<code>hexo clean</code>和<code>hexo douban</code>运行完之后，接着运行部署到github的命令<code>hexo deploy</code>，结果报错了，后面找了很多方法没什么用，就自己按照上面的命令试了一遍，没有报错，所以运行命令如上</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
